text: "Peg" is a 1977 song by Steely Dan and is taken from their sixth studio album Aja. It went to number 7 in Canada, number 8 on the Cash Box chart, number 11 in the United States and number 30 on the Easy Listening chart. It was covered by Nerina Pallot in 2007 and in 2014 by Donny Osmond. == References == Category:1977 songs Category:Art pop songs Category:Steely Dan songs Category:Donny Osmond songs
